title: Evoland v1.1.2490-GOG
description:
Evoland (c) Shiro Games

Release Date : 12/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure, RPG, Indie
Game Version : 1.1.2490
Languages : EN/FR/DE

Evoland is a journey through the history of action/adventure gaming,
allowing you to unlock new technologies, gameplay systems and graphic
upgrades as you progress through the game. Inspired by many cult
series that have left their mark in the RPG video gaming culture,
Evoland takes you from monochrome to full 3D graphics and from active
time battles to real time boss fights, all with plenty of humor and
references to many classic games.
